  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Simulated Valuation</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio6dfbc5536a51204be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Simulated Valuation </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can use this query to simulate a valuation run for selected positions.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The report contains all the relevant position information in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Accounting</span> area.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Integration\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Integration</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> This report is a query. The query is based on InfoSet CFM_POS_11, which, in turn, is based on logical database FTI_TR_POSITIONS.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The technical name of this query is CFM_POS_11.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Features\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Features</h2>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Selection</span>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"b6fac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Product Groups</a>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"ddfac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Selections</a>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"adfac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Control Parameters</a>\n</p></li></ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Output</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The list is displayed using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP List Viewer</span> .\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also:</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4dd40b7ac2234be2e10000000a42189c.html\" title=\"\">SAP List Viewer for SAP GUI (Classic)</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}